      "text": [
        " أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ حَلَفَ فَقَالَ لاَ وَ رَبِّ اَلْمُصْحَفِ فَعَلَيْهِ كَفَّارَةٌ وَاحِدَةٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4332 - Commander of the Faithful (as) said:\n\"Whoever takes an oath and says, 'No, by the Lord (azj) of the Mushaf (the Quran),' must offer a single expiation.\""
        ]
      }
